{:title "PII Scanning and Redaction (Advanced)"
 :description "Detects and transforms sensitive data, including high-entropy strings (API keys) and context-aware PII."
 :philosophy "Shannon Entropy (for secrets), Data-driven (EDN), Simple regex (java.util.regex)."
 :inspired-by "Talon (Patterns), OWASP Top 10 for LLM (2025)"
 :implementation-strategy
 {:recognizers-path "config/pii-patterns.edn"
  :core-fn "mcp-injector.pii/scan-and-redact"
  :entropy-threshold 3.5
  :modes [:mask :hash :replace :block]}
 :acceptance-criteria
 ["Redaction is a pure function: (String, Config) -> {:text String :detected [Keyword]}."
  "Identify common EU PII (Email, IBAN, Phone, VAT, IP) via regex."
  "Detect high-entropy strings (API keys, credentials) via Shannon entropy calculations."
  "Flag environment variable leakage (matching current ENV values)."
  "Scrub messages in `prepare-llm-request` and `execute-tool`."]
 :edge-cases
 ["False positives in Base64 or binary data (add entropy filters)."
  "Multimodal data (out of scope)."
  "Performance on large context windows (chunk scanning)."]
 :depends-on []}
